				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "{{gtClass:GtLMagritteToolForMethodsSource}} is a typical tool and can serve as blueprint for most tools:\n- It relies on Magritte descriptions to define the arguments. A sample is at {{gtMethod:GtLMagritteToolForMethodsSource>>#methodDescriptorsDescription}}. \n- It returns a result object that is also annotated with Magritte descriptions. A sample is at {{gtClass:GtLMethodsWithSource}}. This object is internally wrapped in a {{gtClass:GtLMagritteBasedModel}}. \n- The logic is implemented in {{gtMethod:GtLAbstractMagritteFunctionTool>>#performToolCall:inContext:}}. Our sample tool implements the logic in {{gtMethod:GtLMagritteToolForMethodsSource>>#privatePerformToolCall:inContext:}}."
			},
